<% provide(:title, 'For Art Lovers') %>

<h1>How it works</h1>

<div class="container center">
  <h2>For Art Lovers</h2>
  <div class="row">
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h2><i class="fa fa-cloud-upload-alt fa-2x text-muted mt-5"></i></h2>
      <h2>1) Scan QR Code</h2>
      <p class="center">You can scan the QR Code that venues display with the artwork.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h2><i class="fa fa-search-location fa-2x text-muted mt-5"></i></h2>
      <h2>2) Browse Exhibitions</h2>
      <p class="center"> You can browse the exhibitions page and discover artists.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h2><i class="fa fa-image fa-2x text-muted mt-5"></i></h2>
      <h2>3) Purchase Art</h2>
      <p class="center">You can purchase art directly via our platform.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="col-lg-3">
      <h2><i class="fa fa-shopping-bag fa-2x text-muted mt-5"></i></h2>
      <h2>4) Pick up Art</h2>
      <p class="center">You can pick up the art you bought directly at the venue (shipping coming soon).</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="center jumbotron">
  <h1>We are making exhibition space more accessible.</h1>
  <h2>
  </h2>

  <%= link_to "Browse Art", art_path, class: "btn btn-primary" %>

  <%= link_to "Exhibitions", exhibitions_path, class: "btn btn-secondary" %>

</div>
